<TEXT>
<P>
Cost of Funds Index Drops: Signaling a drop in rates on adjustable-rate 
mortgages, the cost of funds index for 11th District savings institutions 
dropped in April to 8.211% from 8.258% in March, the Federal Home Loan Bank of 
San Francisco reported. Changes in interest rates for ARMs are frequently tied 
to changes in the index. 
</P>
