<P>
Pic 'N' Save Wins Restraining Order: U.S. District Court Judge Robert C. Bonner 
granted Pic 'N' Save's request for a temporary restraining order against Girard 
Partners, prohibiting the investment group from soliciting votes until June 5. 
Pic 'N' Save sued Girard, accusing the La Jolla-based partnership of violating 
federal securities laws in its fight to seize control of the company. A hearing 
on the Dominguez-based retailer's motion for a preliminary injunction is set 
for June 5. 
</P>
