<P>
TELEPHONE COMPLAINT CALLS 
</P>
<P>
October-December, 1989 
</P>
<P>
The airport's noise abatement office logs noise complaints from local citizens. 
During the fourth quarter of 1989, the office received 516 noise complaints 
from local citizens, an 18% decrease from the number of complaints received the 
previous quarter and a 36% decrease compared to the fourth quarter of 1988. A 
total of 3,209 telephone complaints were received in 1989. 
</P>
